      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Lead too short|date=June 2009}}
{{Infobox musical artist  &lt;!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians --&gt;
| Name                = Chris Cunningham
| Img                 = 
| Img_capt            = 
